ooling.com%2Fabout_goodman.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJohn+B.+Goodman+%28industrialist%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=861&amp;dat=20041122&amp;id=PQJZAAAAIBAJ&amp;sjid=C0YNAAAAIBAJ&amp;pg=6091,5175866\">\"Houston-based air conditioner maker sold for $1.43 billion\"</a>. <i>The Victoria Advocate</i>. 22 November 2004<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 October</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Victoria+Advocate&amp;rft.atitle=Houston-based+air+conditioner+maker+sold+for+%241.43+billion&amp;rft.date=2004-11-22&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.google.com%2Fnewspapers%3Fnid%3D861%26dat%3D20041122%26id%3DPQJZAAAAIBAJ%26sjid%3DC0YNAAAAIBAJ%26pg%3D6091%2C5175866&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJohn+B.+Goodman+%28industrialist%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Tom Fowler (20 November 2004). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chron.com/CDA/archives/archive.mpl/2004_3820077/good-deal-for-goodman-company-goes-for-a-cool-1-43.html\">\"GOOD DEAL FOR GOODMAN / Company goes for a cool $1.43 billion / Air conditioner maker, a family-owned firm, expects no big changes\"</a>. Houston Chronicle<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 October</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2F